title: NFL ATL: Summer trade targets

description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- continues its comprehensive analysis of offseason activity, discussing the most enticing summertime trade targets across the NFL.
